node.text:
1993 Nissan Skyline R32 GTST RB20 drift car
By @monkylondon
⠀
Spec list:
Rb20det engine.
Rb25 turbo with enlarged compressor wheel, 360 bearings and steel internals.
Gizmo boost controller
Hks air filter
Big front mount
Big ally rad
Oil cooler
Oil filter relocation
Full 3 inch exhaust system (no boxes).
R32 gtr fuel pump
Bee*r limiter with launch control on handbrake.
Boost and oil temp gauges.
Bride seat.
Drift button handbrake.
Driftworks adjustable camber arms rear.
Hicas lockout.
Adjustable camber arms up front.
Tein coilovers
Drilled and grooved brakes on the front.
Battery relocated to boot.
Gtr overfenders.
Omp wheel and boss.
Viper alarm system.
Cooling Fan on switch.
Nismo short shift
Welded diff
Strut brace
⠀
